<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <% include partials/head %>
  </head>
  <body class="app">
    <header>
      <% include partials/header %>
    </header>

    <main class="home">
      <div class="hero">
        <h2>Generate forms and get leads</h2>
        <h4>Form Crow is an embeddable web form that makes lead collection simple.</h4>
        <img src="/images/SimplifyForms.svg" />
      </div>

        <h3>Get Started in 5 minutes</h3>
        <div class="instruction">
          <div class="instruction__circle"><span class="instruction__number">1</span></div>
          <span class="instruction__step">Ask your customers the right question</span>
        </div>
        <script src='formcrow.com/widget/formcrow.js'></script>
        <form-crow query="What would help your business get more leads?" prime_color="#6399A8" uid="5b3dea9e20917170ee2eb3a7"/></form-crow>
        <img class="home__try" width=150 src="/images/TryIt.svg" />

        <div class="instruction">
          <div class="instruction__step">Generate the simple 2 lines of code<div class="instruction__circle"><span class="instruction__number">2</span></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="home__code">
          <div class="code__header">
            <div class="code__button--red">
            </div>
            <div class="code__button--yellow">
            </div>
            <div class="code__button--green">
            </div>
            <span>2-lines-of-code.html</span>
          </div>
          <div class="code__body">
            <code>&lt;script src='formcrow.com/widget/formcrow.js'>&lt;/script></code>
            <br><br>
            <code>&lt;form-crow query="What would help your business get more leads?" prime_color="#001D2E"/>&lt;/form-crow></code>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="instruction">
          <div class="instruction__circle"><span class="instruction__number">3</span></div>
          <span class="instruction__step">Embed and enjoy</span>
        </div>
        <p>Form Crow is the easiest way to open a conversation with website visitors. Hook users with an engaging question and enjoy real answers. These generated forms are for folk who need leads without wasting time. Get up and running in 5 minutes.</p>

      <% include partials/home/cards %>

    </main>

    <footer>
      <% include partials/footer %>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
